{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_09_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "明日は地方の音楽フェスに出演して\n明後日が新曲のMV撮影……",
      "startTime": 3.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "それで、琴乃ちゃんだけこれから現地に向かって\nフェス紹介の生放送特番に出演、ですよね",
      "startTime": 10.6666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.8666668256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃のスケジュールまで把握してるのはさすがだな",
      "startTime": 14.8666668256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても……相当忙しいのに\n地方のフェス出演に五人とも乗り気なのは驚いたよ",
      "startTime": 21.9333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.9333323479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも沢山の人に私達の歌を届けたいですから\nこれくらい平気ですよ",
      "startTime": 30.5333324432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.7666650455
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "少しでも沢山の人に……か。琴乃も\n同じようなことを言ってたよ。二人とも頼もしいな",
      "startTime": 37.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そ、そうなんですか？\nえへへ……ちょっと照れちゃいますね",
      "startTime": 45.0999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.3666651408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "こほん。えぇっと……私達四人は\n明日の朝に新幹線で向かうんですよね",
      "startTime": 54.7333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。慌ただしくなってすまないが\n現地で合流しよう",
      "startTime": 60.8999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.6333352726
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。沙季ちゃんが当日の予定を\n組んでくれてるので、大丈夫だと思います",
      "startTime": 65.6666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.1333312035
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、フェスか～。出番が終わったら\n会場をゆっくり回ってみたいですね",
      "startTime": 73.7666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7333286604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで出店にも行ってみたいな～\n有名なご当地グルメも出てるらしいですよ！",
      "startTime": 79.499995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、今晩の琴乃ちゃんの生放送出演を\n絶対チェックしないとですね！　録画もしなきゃ！",
      "startTime": 86.5666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "本当にブレないな、渚は",
      "startTime": 90.3999953271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.6666619938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ、大事に思ってるって言ったじゃないですか\n私は琴乃ちゃんのファン第一号ですから",
      "startTime": 98.8333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.6333342553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "特番のナビゲーター役として頑張る琴乃ちゃんの姿……\nすっごく楽しみなんですよ～！",
      "startTime": 107.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。それじゃあ俺は琴乃と先に向かうよ\n今日の仕事も頑張ってくれ",
      "startTime": 115.0666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0999963444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "はい、行ってらっしゃい！\n明日は楽しみましょうね",
      "startTime": 119.2000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――音楽フェス当日",
      "startTime": 122.433329773,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rain-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1133.3384196000084,
          "startTime": 123.5666681926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 123.5000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 123.5000015259
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 123.5666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まずいな、月ストのステージの直前だっていうのに\n雨足がだいぶ強くなってきた",
      "startTime": 128.5666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 131.4333389282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、もうステージまで十五分しかないのに\nまだ渚達四人が会場に着いてないだなんて……",
      "startTime": 135.1666722615,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4120.785395399991,
          "startTime": 139.2874576569
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7066.662597700002,
          "startTime": 142.2333348592
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9099.995931100011,
          "startTime": 144.2666681926
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_fessmall-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "fessmall-01-evening",
      "startTime": 141.7666721662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　渚から電話だ！\nもしもし、今どこにいるんだ！？",
      "startTime": 144.5666722615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7333358764
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.7333358764
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、すみません！\n今、最寄り駅の、駅ビルにいます",
      "startTime": 150.7666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2666599592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "大雨で新幹線が大幅に遅れてしまって\nさっき着いたところなんです！",
      "startTime": 157.4666681926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.8000054996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "しかも冠水してるみたいで、その影響で渋滞が酷くて\nタクシーも遅れてて……",
      "startTime": 164.6666803996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "会場に着いたら急いで準備しますけど……\n月ストの出番には間に合わないかもしれません",
      "startTime": 170.7333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.5666742008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくのライブなのに……ごめんなさい……",
      "startTime": 175.5666742008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_mall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "mall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.133342902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "渚達は悪くないよ。ちょっとどうするか考えるから……\nえ？　琴乃？　任せるって……どういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 185.0000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
